com.vector.cfg.persistency.filters

Interface IPersistencyExportFilter


  • @PublishedApi(value=CHANGES_FORBIDDEN)
public interface IPersistencyExportFilter
    IPersistencyExportFilter specifies an interface to export parts of the internal model. Please use the IPersistencyExportFilterFactory to get some convenience implementations.

    Remark

    Implementations of this interface usually implement a static view on the model. They are not intended to supervise model changes. This means that a filter instance may become invalid when the model changes!
